                     <interp inst="t18230409-165-person1509" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 26th of March, I apprehended Wiggins, and told him it was for the watch - he said</p>
               <p>"Oh! it is for that, is it."</p>
               <p>CROSS - GUILTY. Aged 19.</p>
